sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Router as Cell Router
    participant Policy as WASM Policy
    participant Service as Business Service
    participant DB as Cell Database
    participant Audit as Audit Aggregator
    
    Note over Client,Audit: Sovereign Request Lifecycle (Total: 168ms)
    
    Client->>Gateway: HTTP Request
    Note right of Gateway: Stage 1: Ingress (5ms)
    Gateway->>Gateway: Validate Schema
    Gateway->>Gateway: Extract TenantID
    Gateway->>Gateway: Check Rate Limit
    
    Note right of Router: Stage 2: Routing (2ms)
    Gateway->>Router: Route Request
    Router->>Router: hash(TenantID) % NUM_CELLS
    
    Note right of Policy: Stage 3: Policy (1ms)
    Router->>Policy: Evaluate Authorization
    Policy->>Policy: Local WASM Execution
    Policy-->>Router: ALLOW
    
    Note right of Service: Stage 4: Business Logic (100ms)
    Router->>Service: Execute Request
    Service->>Service: Domain Logic
    Service->>Service: Cache Lookup
    
    Note right of DB: Stage 5: Persistence (50ms)
    Service->>DB: Write Data
    DB->>DB: Replicate to 2 Replicas
    DB-->>Service: Commit Confirmed
    
    Note right of Gateway: Stage 6: Response (10ms)
    Service-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK
    
    Gateway--)Audit: Async Audit Log
    Note right of Audit: Out-of-band, non-blocking
    
    Note over Client,Audit: Total: 5+2+1+100+50+10 = 168ms (< 200ms target)
